# Docs
- README mit Setup, Env, Deploy, Rollen.  
- Separate Guides: `docs/admin.md`, `docs/mitarbeiter.md`.
- SOTA Best Practices: Architektur-Dokumentation.
- DSGVO-Compliance: Datenschutz-Dokumentation.
- API-Dokumentation: Firebase Services, React Query.  

# CI/CD
- GitHub Actions: Build + Firebase Deploy bei Push auf main.  
- PRs: Lint + Typecheck + Build + Tests. Preview Deploy optional.
- Bundle-Analyse: Chunk-Größen überwachen.
- Performance-Tests: Lighthouse CI Integration.
- Security-Scans: Dependency-Vulnerabilities prüfen.  

# Branching
- feat/..., fix/..., chore/...  
- PR-Template mit Checkliste (Tests, Screenshots, Migration).
- SOTA Workflow: Conventional Commits, Semantic Versioning.
- Code Review: SOTA Best Practices prüfen.
- Performance-Budget: Bundle-Größen-Limits.
